{
  "stem": "20711.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My aunts and uncle gave us extra food to the trip, but we tried not to take too much because it was a long walk.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I recall that walk back home, there was still a lot of shooting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The front was not too far away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some of those guns' bullet went above our head.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was scared, and my father said, no, they are far away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You just think it's close.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They convinced me they are far, but I know they were not very far away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We spend the first night with that friend who-- who helped me escape the very first time with the motorcycle.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because the walk was too long to do it during a day and there was a curfew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You had to be inside a house before sundown.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We knew we're never going to make it all the way home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So halfway we stopped, and we stayed overnight to his house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then we followed next day, the road and went all the way home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was an interesting episode once we reached the town, though we were all very happy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were walking on the beginning of the main street, and there was some peasant womans who passed us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They greeting us, said hello.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But kind of strange look on their face.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And just when they passed, I noticed they dropped something on the floor, on the ground, and it was one of my doll.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Nobody had a doll like that, not in that town, and I recognized it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I looked at my mom.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She looked at me, and she pulled my sleeves to point me, don't say anything, and we did not.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "When we got close to the house, we saw it was completely destroyed.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
